<para>
  Next, answer the following questions.
</para>

<orderedlist>
  <listitem>
    When I assign a reading, what should you do other than just read 
    the material?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    What happens if you turn in homework late?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    Explain what an eboard is (or seems to be) and list a few ways one
