  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    How can you figure out what assignments you have due?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    When can you work with other students and when can you not work with
    other students?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    How can you obtain help from me?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    Other than simply selecting <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> from the
    <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu, are there other things you should do
    (or think about doing), when printing documents for this class?
  </listitem>

  <listitem>
    Do you agree to abide by my
    <ulink url="../handouts/academic-honesty.html">policies on
